Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did a CP-0 knock out another CP-0?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my place to say something, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...is it okay for you to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Roronoa Zoro, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't understand\Nthe ways of the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And that skeleton right there\Nis Soul King, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to stay there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thump!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, in many ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what's going on?\NDid you have a falling out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I did it for a purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I won't harm you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't trust someone\Nwho betrays their friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Stussy.\NI put both of them to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have brought down\Nthe Government's people!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it from?! Your ally?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rob Lucci has been taken down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even that shrewd Lucci didn't see it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are Zoro and Brook okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm as good as new!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay on your guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:04:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, great! Stussy did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,York, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,York, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with me! York!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't eat anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just talking in her sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up now! Something big is happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, who is Stussy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She took down those two.\NShe must be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,For an undercover operation\Nlasting over 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,she has been our ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You sent a spy\Ninto an intelligence agency?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And for more than 20 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what we planned...\NBut it ended up that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, Doctor...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My authority is the same as Lucci's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't override his orders\Nto the Seraphim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You did enough! Stussy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stop them at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, we gotta stop those brats or\Nour friends will all end up being buried!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But those kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't they look familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you do that, you brats?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:06:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You messed up the lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But that made it easier to get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No! That'll cause trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I got out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Seraphim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When I look closely...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you're more of a human than he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Lilith?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Seraphim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Edison!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Edison!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Lilith-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you worrying about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Edison!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,--That was close!\N--Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,--I thought that was really it!\N--Edison! You scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Those look-alikes, they stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Who the hell are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!\NThey're my warriors who I'm quite proud of!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not gonna attack us anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Our rank of authority is higher than CP-0\Nand we commanded them directly,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,so the order to the Seraphim\Nhas been overwritten.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too hard for you to understand,\NMosshead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being annoying, you stupid cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Zoro-phim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't treat me like the Seraphim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,--Stop, Green-phim!\N--Shut up, Twirly-phim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,--What should we do now?\N--I'll kill you, Directionally-challenged-phim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been entrusted with an important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's work as one\Nand help Vegapunk off the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You're full of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Super!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can breathe a little easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Those Seraphim are threatening\Nwhen they're our enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's great to have them on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We have some quite dependable allies now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shaka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I put Sea Prism Stone Cuffs\Non Lucci and Kaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So even if they wake up,\Nthey can't use their Devil Fruit powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Stussy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to get off of the island\Nby ship with the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey! You just invited one more person\Nto come aboard the Sunny!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stussy-sama is coming with us, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's join everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonney! Old Man Punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see them anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange! Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go check this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Man Punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't set sail without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saving Bonney led the Straw Hats\Nto the Future Island Egghead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They met Dr. Vegapunk\Nand his six Satellites{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and learned about the advanced civilization\Nfrom 900 years ago{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the truth about the ones\Nwho inherited Ohara's will.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After being asked to by Vegapunk Stella,\NLuffy decided to take them all to sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to take me away\Nfrom Egghead-{\i1}Quasar{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, they got into a battle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...against CP-0 led by Rob Lucci\Nwho came to the island to kill Vegapunk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After subduing Lucci and Kaku,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Luffy and the others\Nwanted to leave Egghead immediately...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But an incident occurred.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr. Vegapunk Stella disappeared!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Sphinx in the New World.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:13:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The pirate Whitebeard's hometown.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Marco. I was really scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, the Navy came surging!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...sorry-yoi\Nthat I wasn't there to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Navy guys were horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they would seize\NWhitebeard's treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They're no different from pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:33.64,On Top,,0,0,0,,SEVERAL DAYS AGO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather all the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't do you any harm\Nas long as you cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This island is not affiliated\Nwith the World Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You people aren't protected by the law!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe Whitebeard's vast treasure\Nis somewhere on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me where it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But we've never heard of his treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a lie!\NWe can't tell you what we don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't tell us,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll consider it an act of treason!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...if I shoot you guys one by one,\Nwill you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There is no such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't point a gun at my little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't pay money to the Government,\Nwe're not even to be treated as humans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You brutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco isn't here to protect you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Restrain her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it! She's an elder!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop it! Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...my daddy's hometown!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Edward Weevil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We gotta run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yeah!\N--H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they sent troops to arrest him\Nwhen the Seven Warlords system was abolished!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't contact those troops now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They must've been beaten! All of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So he is as strong as a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat to the ship!\NWe'll wait for reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:17:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Sphinx!\NWe were attacked by a former Warlord Weevil!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We need backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Navy soldiers\Nwho came raiding the village left the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for that huge man,\Nwe would have been done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,--Right?\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's a hero.\NI'm really glad that you're all okay-yoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think came after that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Navy Admiral Ryokugyu came...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And though Weevil resisted,\Nthey took him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Weevil!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me back my son! And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:51.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,MISS BUCKIN, FREELOADER AT MADS,\NSELF-PROCLAIMED SCIENTIST,\NEX-ROCKS PIRATES MEMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...give us\N"Whitebeard" Edward Newgate's heritage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:55.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,REAL NAME\NBUCKINGHAM STUSSY
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you really came here for-yoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:17:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to jail defending his father's village!\NWhat an admirable boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and Newgate's son!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate him\Nfor defending the village-yoi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You also don't believe Weevil is\NWhitebeard's real son, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There is someone who can prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Dr. Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizaru-san! We brought some teacakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:57.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you tested them for poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take them. You can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,May I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you a little something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever met Dr. Vegapunk before?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just once, a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...he betrayed you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:04.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,ST. JAYGARCIA SATURN OF THE FIVE ELDERS\NHIGHEST AUTHORITIES OF THE WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly feel what has happened is a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far I have run{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:21.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doredake hashitte kita noka{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without knowing it, I counted scars{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}wakaranai mama kizuato kazoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A treasure map in my head all along{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:35.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}zutto atama no naka ni aru takara no chizu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still looking for the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mirai wo sagashi tsuzuketeru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:49.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hontou no yakusoku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lies much deeper in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:56.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mune no oku no motto oku ni aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dream that no one can catch up with{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:05.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}dare mo mina oitsukenai yume{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all I hold on to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:11.14,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitotsu dakishimete{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To you who smiles like the sun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:18.23,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}taiyou no youni warau anata e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll sing the same song as that day{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:25.15,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ano hi to onaji uta wo utau yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This wish I don't want to forget even when I grow up{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}otona ni nattemo wasuretakunai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until it reaches you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kono negai ga todoku made{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dive into the Sea of Information!\NThe Punk Records Library!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Lilith, one of the Satellites of\NDr. Vegapunk, the genius scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:22:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Edison, also Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we'll introduce this one! Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.28,0:22:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the former 1st division commander\Nand ship's doctor of the Whitebeard Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,who uses the Tweet-Tweet Fruit,\NMythical Type, Phoenix Model.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He was born on October 5th\Nand likes pineapples!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Paramount War,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,he fought against Navy Admirals\Nto defend Ace and Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't reach...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...the {\i1}king{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.47,0:22:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...so easily-{\i1}yoi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He lost Whitebeard,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and ever since the Whitebeard Pirates\Nwere scattered in the Grudge War,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,he has been defending Sphinx,\NWhitebeard's hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But when the Straw Hats set out\Nto defeat Kaido,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.03,0:22:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,he went to the Land of Wano\Nand helped them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If my captain gives the order, I'll just follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.45,0:22:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on Straw Hat, too.\NNo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.08,0:23:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,On you guys from the Worst Generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.29,0:23:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For the Straw Hats,\Nhe is someone who can always be counted on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.84,0:23:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look forward to seeing more of him\Nin the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.72,0:23:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.30,0:23:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen it,\Ndonate to our research fund!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.26,0:23:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.73,0:23:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the brink of escaping Egghead,\NDr. Vegapunk, the key figure in the mission,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.02,0:23:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}suddenly and inexplicably disappears!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where in the closed laboratory did he go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Straw Hats, who have been left behind,\Nbegin their search for the genius scientist!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.20,0:23:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Trouble Occurs! Seek Dr. Vegapunk!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.79,0:23:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.71,0:23:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.71,0:23:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,
